description: Returns the list of all event objects in a calendar view defined by a time range.

properties.name: startDateTime
properties.description: The start date and time of the time range, represented in ISO 8601 format using the UTC timezone. For example, "2019-11-08T19:00:00-08:00".

properties.name: endDateTime
properties.description: The end date and time of the time range, represented in ISO 8601 format using the UTC timezone. For example, "2019-11-08T20:00:00-08:00".
